column3: VOLUNTARY PARTICIPATION: Your participation in this study is voluntary. It is up to you to decide whether or not to take part in this study. If you decide to take part in this study, you will be asked to sign a consent form. After you sign the consent form, you are still free to withdraw at any time, without reason. Withdrawing from this study will not the affect the relationship you have, if any, with the researcher. If you withdraw from the study before you have submitted the from, your data will not be collected. You MUST be 16 years or older to participate
